
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 100px;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #666;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

            a:hover {
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: #fff;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.</p>
        <a asp-controller="Admin" asp-action="Index">Go back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
